01:21:43,700 --> 01:21:44,860
What now?

1072
01:21:44,940 --> 01:21:46,780
Word travels fast in my circles.

1073
01:21:46,860 --> 01:21:50,860
Word is, a cutter came in
for a synth tattoo.

1074
01:21:50,940 --> 01:21:54,260
Word is that cutter is you.

1075
01:21:54,340 --> 01:21:57,220
You saw that implant.
It was destroyed. It's useless.

1076
01:21:57,260 --> 01:21:59,140
You.

1077
01:21:59,180 --> 01:22:02,380
Bannister's footage is gone,
but you've seen his life.

1078
01:22:02,420 --> 01:22:05,220
It's encrypted
into your implant.

1079
01:24:38,180 --> 01:24:40,380
Will you look at that?

1080
01:25:15,620 --> 01:25:17,260
Come and get me.

1081
01:25:20,300 --> 01:25:22,260
He had a very big meeting
one day...

1082
01:25:22,380 --> 01:25:24,660
but he took me
horseback riding instead.

1083
01:25:24,740 --> 01:25:27,500
He would read me stories
every night.

1084
01:25:27,580 --> 01:25:30,100
Sometimes he would make it up
as he went along...

1085
01:25:30,180 --> 01:25:32,540
and I knew, but I didn't care.

1086
01:25:32,580 --> 01:25:35,540
Your mom said I was here
to talk about your dad.

1087
01:25:35,620 --> 01:25:37,620
We don't need to do that
if you don't want to.

1088
01:25:37,700 --> 01:25:39,980
- Daddy?
- Yes, sweetie?

1089
01:25:40,060 --> 01:25:41,860
- Alan, please!
- I want to go back to bed.

1090
01:25:41,940 --> 01:25:43,700
- It's John's birthday.
- We'll have meatballs.

1091
01:25:43,740 --> 01:25:46,220
Italian. You love Italian.
A toast.

1092
01:25:46,300 --> 01:25:48,900
- Happy birthday, John.
- Happy birthday, Fletcher.

1093
01:25:48,940 --> 01:25:50,100
Thanks, Alan.

1094
01:25:50,180 --> 01:25:53,620
Alan, put the newspaper down.
Come on.

1095
01:25:53,740 --> 01:25:56,900
You gonna lighten up
and be gay for a moment?

1096
01:26:15,940 --> 01:26:18,180
It's for the greater good, Alan.

1097
01:26:18,260 --> 01:26:20,580
Your life will mean something.

1098
01:26:22,540 --> 01:26:24,260
I promise.

